        </li>
        <li>
          <p>Browser and device information</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>Session replay data (if enabled)</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>Performance metrics</p>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>Better Together configures Sentry to exclude personally identifiable information where possible. For more information about Sentry's data practices, see <a href="https://sentry.io/privacy/">Sentry's privacy policy</a>.</p>

