      <p><a id="heading--marketing"></a></p>
      <h2 id="does-bts-use-personal-information-for-marketing-purposes">Does Better Together use personal information for marketing purposes?</h2>

      <p>Better Together may use personal information about our customers and prospective customers in order to directly market our own services and inform you about new products and features that we offer. We also use the information you give to sign up for our mailing lists and announcements to send those messages.</p>

