        </li>
        <li>
          <p><strong>Session Data</strong>: Expired automatically (session cookies expire on browser close; invitation tokens expire after 30 minutes to 24 hours depending on type)</p>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>After you close your account, your data is either deleted or anonymized according to the platform's configuration.</p>

      <p><a id="heading--gdpr"></a></p>
      <h2 id="does-bts-comply-with-the-eu-general-data-protection-regulation">Does Better Together comply with the EU General Data Protection Regulation?</h2>

      <p>Better Together respects privacy rights under <a href="https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=uriserv:OJ.L_.2016.119.01.0001.01.ENG">Regulation (EU) 2016/679</a>, the European Union's General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). Information that GDPR requires Better Together to give can be found throughout this privacy notice, including information on the <a href="#heading--gdpr-rights">rights of data subjects</a>.</p>

